Embed Einstein Predictions in Tableau Flows

Use the Prediction step in Tableau Prep to include Einstein Discovery predictions directly into your flows. Enrich your flow output with predictions and, optionally, improvements and top factors.

Add a Prediction Step to a Flow
Connect to Salesforce with a user account that can access Einstein Discovery.
Select one deployed prediction definition from Salesforce.
Map model fields to flow fields and configure other settings as needed.

When the flow is run, the Prediction step gets a prediction for each row of data and saves the prediction value, and optionally other information, to the flow output.
title: Embedding Einstein Predictions in Tableau Flows
